            <title><![CDATA[Switch price increase announced for the U.S.]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/08/switch-price-increase-announced-for-the-us</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/switch-price-increase-announced-for-the-u-s.1259592/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Switch 2 systems, Switch 2 and Switch software, and Nintendo Switch Online memberships not affected.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Platforms > Nintendo [22,402 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo">Nintendo</a> will increase the price of the original Switch family of systems in the United States based on market conditions, effective August 3, Nintendo of America <a href="https://www.nintendo.com/us/whatsnew/nintendo-switch-pricing-update/" target="_blank">announced</a>. <span id="more-981466"></span></p><p>Affected products include Switch – OLED Model, Switch, Switch Lite, and select Switch accessories.</p><p>Other products, including certain <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [286 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a> accessories, amiibo, and Nintendo Sound Clock: Alarmo, will also experience price changes.</p><p>Pricing for Switch 2 systems, Switch 2 and Switch software, and <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,424 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Nintendo Switch</a> Online memberships will not be affected.</p><p>The pricing update in the United States follows a <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/switch-price-increase-announced-for-canada">similar pricing change</a> that recently went in effect for Canada.</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/08/switch-price-increase-announced-for-the-us]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
