            <title><![CDATA[Silent Hill f hands-on previews]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/08/silent-hill-f-hands-on-previews</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/silent-hill-f-hands-on-previews.1259532/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Media plays five hours of the upcoming horror game.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Several outlets have gone up with first hands-on previews of <em><a title="Games > Silent Hill f [5 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/silent-hill-f">Silent Hill f</a></em>, which include new gameplay footage. <span id="more-981456"></span></p><p>English previews are available at <a href="https://gameinformer.com/preview/2025/08/01/when-beauty-is-the-beast" target="_blank">Game Informer</a>, <a href="https://www.gamerbraves.com/silent-hill-f-preview-japanese-horror-brought-to-life-in-this-fresh-take-on-the-classic-series/" target="_blank">GamerBraves</a>, <a href="https://www.gamesradar.com/video/vRaaC7bl/we-ve-played-silent-hill-f-and-it-s-made-us-excited-for-the-series-future/" target="_blank">GamesRadar</a>, <a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/silent-hill-f-we-played-it-for-5-hours" target="_blank">IGN</a>, and <a href="https://www.polygon.com/silent-hill-f-hands-on-preview-release-date/" target="_blank">Polygon</a>. Japanese previews are available at <a href="https://www.4gamer.net/games/664/G066418/20250728020/" target="_blank">4Gamer.net</a> (<a href="https://www.4gamer.net/games/664/G066418/20250728023/" target="_blank">2</a>), <a href="https://www.famitsu.com/article/202508/48385" target="_blank">Famitsu</a> (<a href="https://www.famitsu.com/article/202508/48377" target="_blank">2</a>), <a href="https://dengekionline.com/article/202508/48301" target="_blank">Dengeki Online</a> (<a href="https://dengekionline.com/article/202508/48211" target="_blank">2</a>), and <a href="https://www.gamer.ne.jp/news/202508010002/" target="_blank">Gamer.ne.jp</a>, <a href="https://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/preview/2034491.html" target="_blank">GAME Watch</a> (2).</p><p><em>Silent Hill f</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,012 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,612 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,792 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2947440/SILENT_HILL_f/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/silent-hill-f-714aed" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Epic Games Store</a>, and <a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/silent-hill-f/9n5nfrqv2hqq" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a> on September 25.</p><p>Watch the footage below.</p><h2><span>Gameplay</span></h2><p><strong>Bahamut</strong></p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><iframe title="4K PS5《沉默之丘 f》12 分鐘實機遊玩 台灣泥巴娛樂團隊製作昭和恐怖壓抑氛圍" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZbdQq0ZCpWc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Dengeki Online</strong></p><p><iframe title="『SILENT HILL f（サイレントヒル f）』先行プレイ映像。日本が舞台の和風サイコロジカルホラー" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6T9gUTPxoCQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>GamesRadar</strong></p><p><iframe title="We’ve played Silent Hill f and it’s made us excited for the series’ future | Silent Hill f preview" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oRvNPbo1ylE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>IGN</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Silent Hill f: What We Think After Playing 5 Hours" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/N-U2xgRtDCg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>IGN Japan</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="和ホラーの新たなる金字塔？『SILENT HILL f』を5時間プレイした感想！" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bU-xTlrWNiU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Ruliweb</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="'사일런트 힐 f' 플레이 영상" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nXdXsogQFJc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/08/silent-hill-f-hands-on-previews]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
