            <title><![CDATA[Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter character trailers – Tita Russell, Zin Vathek]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/08/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-character-trailers-tita-russell-zin-vathek</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-character-trailers-%E2%80%93-tita-russell-zin-vathek.1259502/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>An engineer and a veteran Bracer.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Nihon Falcom [745 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/nihon-falcom">Falcom</a> has released the seventh and eighth character trailers for <em><a title="Games > Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter [18 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter">Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter</a></em>, introducing Tita Russell and Zin Vathek. <span id="more-981444"></span></p><p>Here is their official descriptions:</p><blockquote><p><strong>Tita Russell</strong></p><p>A diligent and hardworking grandaughter of an orbal scientist.</p><p>The granddaughter of the Orbment scientist, Professor Russell. Warm and cheerful, she has an earnest, pure-hearted nature that makes her beloved by all.</p><p>Born into a family of engineers, she has a deep love for machines. Her only flaw is that she loses sight of her surroundings while tinkering with them.</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p>Estelle and Joshua start doting on Tita soon after their first meeting, and she eventually grows to think of them as the older siblings she never had.</p><p><strong>Zin Vathek</strong></p><p>A veteran Bracer with a formidable physique from the Calvard Republic.</p><p>A veteran Bracer from the Calvard Republic who has mastered the Taito Style, one of the three great eastern martial arts styles.</p><p>Despite his massive, bear-like build, he has a warm and easygoing personality. He is a reliable, big brother figure. However, he has a soft spot for women.</p><p>Originally came to the Liberl Kingdom to compete in a martial arts tournament by himself. However, after lending a hand to Estelle and Joshua during their travels, he decides to team up with them instead.</p></blockquote><p><em>Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,012 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,424 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,792 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3375780/Trails_in_the_Sky_1st_Chapter/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on September 19 worldwide. Read more about the game <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/03/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-main-characters-voice-cast">here</a>, <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/05/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-rolent-characters-and-places-battle-system">here</a>, <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-bose-characters-and-places-location-trailers">here</a>, <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-tactical-orbments">here</a>, and <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-ruan-characters-and-places-trailer">here</a>.</p><p>Watch the trailers below.</p><h2><span>Character Trailer: Tita Russell</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="Tita Character Trailer - Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_JiNhqXXfuw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="【ティータ】キャラクタームービー #空の軌跡the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/euJquxrAPJM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Korean</strong></p><p><iframe title="【티타】 캐릭터 무비 #하늘의궤적 #the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/EqfKWJzaiW4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Traditional Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【缇妲】 角色视频 #空之轨迹the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/5Dn0jysFB2w?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Simplified Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【緹妲】 角色影片 #空之軌跡the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zDu2-F_zo48?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><h2><span>Character Trailer: Zin Vathek</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Zin Character Trailer - Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/__TWLm05Uf8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【ジン】キャラクタームービー #空の軌跡the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/H_Pww2QsUWk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Korean</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【진】 캐릭터 무비 #하늘의궤적 #the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yp6OasJuWKk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Traditional Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【陣】 角色影片 #空之軌跡the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gJ7eHU0X3WQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Simplified Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【阵】 角色视频 #空之轨迹the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LNdqMJeggOw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/08/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-character-trailers-tita-russell-zin-vathek]]></content:encoded>
